Explosivo
=========

A physics-based 2D art program written in C++.

The code isn't pretty but it's a work-in-progress and will get better as I go.  Really!

Required Libraries
------------------

* Antigrain
* FreeType 2
* jnetlib
* libpng
* zlib

These are all included in the Explosivo directory.

Compiling Explosivo
-------------------

It's easy.  The two build configurations I've setup are Debug and Release, with the rest being not-working defaults supplied by the IDE.  All you need to do is choose a config and build!

